      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为CloudNative_K8sCluster项目画一个Git流程图，展示从main分支合并到未开发分支的过程。标题就叫\"Merge from main onto undeveloped branch (CloudNative_K8sCluster)\"吧。",
