    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "用develop分支就行，它在这里就是代表那个待开发的特性分支。流程应该是：先在main上提交，然后切出develop分支做开发，同时main继续往前走，最后把main的新内容合并回develop。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "commit",
        "checkout",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我来画这个LR横向的Git图。先画main上的初始commit，然后branch出develop分支，develop上做一个commit，接着checkout回main再做commit，最后checkout develop把main合并进来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "branch develop",
        "checkout main",
        "checkout develop",
        "merge main"
