      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个顺序。让我确认一下：develop分支上的commit要先于main的第二个commit，这样合并的时候才能体现出main有新内容需要同步过来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "main",
        "commit顺序"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，我发现刚才的顺序有问题。如果develop先commit，然后checkout main再commit，这样develop和main就分叉了。但按照您的需求，应该是main持续演进，develop需要追赶main。我调整一下：develop的commit在切出后就做，然后main继续commit，最后merge。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch develop",
        "commit",
        "checkout main",
        "commit",
        "merge main"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
